  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this exciting first-person VR game, become a parkour hero, swiftly swinging through the city using spider silk, collecting scattered coins in mid-air. Master the swinging technique and navigate through urban landscapes, collecting as many coins as possible.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An affordable and easy-to-learn first-person VR collection game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game tracks your collected coin count, providing a sense of achievement and challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing urban environment offers an immersive gaming experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports SteamVR, Pico 3/4.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this exciting first-person VR game, become a parkour hero, swiftly swinging through the city using spider silk, collecting scattered coins in mid-air. Master the swinging technique and navigate through urban landscapes, collecting as many coins as possible.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An affordable and easy-to-learn first-person VR collection game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game tracks your collected coin count, providing a sense of achievement and challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing urban environment offers an immersive gaming experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports SteamVR, Pico 3/4.</p></li></ul>",
